Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便就给人家取名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就只是一个torch而已还自认为了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不需要那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于完成使命的flamehaze来说 名字这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是个奇怪的torch啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前看到的torch 一告诉他们发生了什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都嚎啕大哭 逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有舍弃这样的身体的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢 因为他是mystes吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 torch的性质是从原来的人那儿继承来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是称为mystes 只要还是torch 这点就不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个身体里的到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是问题不在那体内的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是盯上了这个的“红世之徒”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和那个是怎么样的torch无关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很快就会消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残留的渣总有一天会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不会记得其存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会留下什么痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记 绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说要看守我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又不在 夏娜她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就飞跑出游戏室了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说去找平井同学 却一直没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池 你还记得平井同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是平井同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能忘记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池 拜托了 把作业的答案告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是洗洗脸再来比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗 当然是看着你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是竟然跟到这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个是平井同学的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井由香里就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我强制挤进了平井由香里的存在里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强制挤进了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用了昨天残余的渣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我现在就是平井由香里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你的样子完全不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 这是之前借给我的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的挤进存在里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非是要看着像以前的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是其它识别平井由香里的“存在” 让我给替换了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了讨灭“徒”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你接受了我们的干涉 所以就感觉奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然在意 平井同学不是昨天刚刚才消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天就侵占了她的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵占？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本人都已经被吞噬而死亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是利用了不会消失的座位而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不合适的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是什么合不合适的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会用这样的口气说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样说别人…我真不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:05:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能理解就说别人差劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是优等生的特权吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且竟然冲着女生大喊大叫简直丢死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才是无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点儿坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在点名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安倍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石井
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上原
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学消失并不是夏娜的错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挤进平井同学的存在里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为了打倒敌人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜她至今一直都在经历这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你打成肉泥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就如那个佐藤说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能理解就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我实在是无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 平井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笔记本和教科书都一直都没翻开 你到底在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井 你听到老师的话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个填空题 完全空在没有意义的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是猜谜 请空在能根据前后文推测的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确的答案就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“That which we call a rose, by any other name would smell as sweet.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是原文没有整个记下来的话 应当是不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是从段落来看 还有两段没完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:07:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然这样说老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你讲解得差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喋喋不休地没个重点说个没完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要教我的话就好好学习后再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 混蛋 简直岂有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 你说我写的化学方程式有哪里不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜 再也不理你们了 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师的说明到底哪儿错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祇园精舍 盛者必衰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那个就是平井？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像特别难接近似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 呼吸都屏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比考试时候还紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 坂井同学 对那个平井同学严厉地指责了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是那个样子 其实是讨人厌的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井 我中午的时候有班委会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我一个人吃没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待会儿跟大家解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的你太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然如此高兴还真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿的甜瓜面包皮的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口感脆脆的真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然torch就是torch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道原因就乱发泄一通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟之前的一样 没什么不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快消灭了“红世之徒”和那个torch分开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要去吗 玛莉安奴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这次一定让我抓住那个mystes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让前几天的失败就这样算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情 我根本没有那么想过的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:11:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我不想只是一味接受主人您那温柔的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您理解我这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可爱的玛莉安奴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是mystes的身边有那个flamehaze
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带上这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉自己就像是快消失的torch
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算消失了 谁也不会认为这很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有人会记得我在这里存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起自己的消失 那样可能更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟被学生如何教导了 大峰老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫平井由香里的可是出名的问题儿童啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没有想到是那样的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能被学生给小看了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她好好见识一下才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午的课上也很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉平井同学到底是何方神圣一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香里 bye-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bye-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:13:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井 补习班上课还早 要不我们去随便吃点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想开解我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是“封绝”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这是学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟地点在哪儿没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是简单就能预想到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 大家都还在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被“封绝”的就是敌人 你和对方说去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样大家都会被牵扯进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直呼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情怎样都无所谓的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西是比还魔术简单的花招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池 池 池…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前的是同一个“磷子”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你主人的名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我会说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是确认一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 竟然犹犹豫豫舍不得扔掉没用的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还真是个大蠢蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏时合适的相遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 这就是“红世之徒”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 竟然用区区一把大刀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就将我引以为豪的宝具RegularSharp减少了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要道歉了 玛莉安奴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你拿着一个不称手的“宝具”真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是她的主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“猎人”Friagne
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:26.52,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字由来: Friagne 旧约伪典、东方正教外典\N“以诺书”(ENOCH)记载的恶魔(堕天使)之一，第五天的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“猎人”？ 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专杀flamehaze的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太喜欢被这样称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是为了收集像这样散落各处的宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才被称做“猎人”的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是名声响彻我们“红世”的“天壤的劫火”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯托尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是第一次见到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事情在这边我早有耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我扯这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱使很多的“宝具”屠杀了数个flamehaze的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常强大的“红世之王”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:16:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的契约者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫作“贽殿遮那”的flamehaze吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟传闻中一样美艳动人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像其实一点儿火也使不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你借助那剑的力量才好不容易唤出火来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“天壤的劫火”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约者是这样弱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法将你“红世”的魔神的力量完全发挥出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能发挥出来你就来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就使得flamehaze暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就爆死的我见得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样让mystes受到破坏 那就本末颠倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会再来拜访的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底那身体里是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是一般的“红世之徒”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把破坏的地方修补好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 我得用他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用他？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用他的“存在之力”将被破坏的地方修补好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用…用池他的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因为没有“红世之徒”吃剩下的torch
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能使用垂死之人的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是人的话 只要一个垂死之人的就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他作为torch来配置的话\N也不会有什么问题不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池他就会像我一样死了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有作为本原的力量的话就没有办法修复了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人的也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 怎么能使用活着的人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是等“封绝”解开的话就会很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人都会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这种事情我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就使用你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剩下的火焰是可以修复这点儿程度的破坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然你作为torch就会更快消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这样做也不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也和其它的torch一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了保存残留的一点火焰而丢人现眼的torch
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 还有这个办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在 为了池他们而使用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我存在过的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 古怪的 不 奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是讨厌的 对 讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当不客气地使用了他的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么办法啊 他自己提出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 也给它保留了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道我们在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直觉 因为感觉到小小的 像今天“封绝”那样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能遇到那种力量的体现也差不多能知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我一直都很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是通信器？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似是而非
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是为了将寄宿她身体里的我的意志“显现”的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:28.21,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显现（けんげん）：在人类世界现身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称为Cocytus的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 好像多少明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只是为这事来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是为今天的事来跟你道歉和道谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉和道谢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不记得有这些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学的事我说得过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有不使用池的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不知道有什么说得过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有使用作为人的池 相对的只是使用了你的“存在之力”而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的火焰已经变得相当小了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失只是时间问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样也比只作为torch被人给遗忘了的好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在 我的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得留在了池他们那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是最后还是和其它的记忆一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湮没于今后将发生的事情中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是还是留下了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都放了糖的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调羹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 干嘛这么着急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 或许在那个mystes身体里的“宝具”就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:21:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己身体里的到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 御崎市的新来者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真是个萧条的城市啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在欧洲那儿我已经听你很多抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说萧条是跟着你来的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我美丽的高脚酒杯马乔莉-冬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 一定是逃进这里没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总感觉有其它什么气息在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 的确有其它气息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你一身酒臭啦 哈哈哈……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我住嘴 笨蛋马尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来稍微有些有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的出现了

