Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.57,0:24:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将她自己逼入了绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.31,0:24:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这时候 flamehaze之间的战斗终于展开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.94,0:24:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 困惑的flamehaze
